  <verse number="6" style="v" />In the same way, encourage the younger men to be sensible.

  <verse number="7" style="v" />In all ways present yourself as a model of good works; and when you teach, show integrity and dignity.

  <verse number="8" style="v" />Speak a message that is healthy and blameless, so that anyone who is opposed may be put to shame, because he has nothing bad to say about us. 
